{"type":"item.completed","item":{"id":"item_2","type":"command_execution","command":"\"C:\\\\Program Files\\\\PowerShell\\\\7\\\\pwsh.exe\" -Command \"Get-Content -Path 'E:\\\\CodeRepo\\\\shop-api\\\\docs\\\\frontend-specs.md'\"","aggregated_output":"# Shop API вҖ” Proposta de UI para Loja Virtual\r\n\r\n## 1. Conceito visual\r\n\r\nA **Shop API** Г© uma loja virtual criada para testar novas tecnologias, mas com estrutura visual e funcional suficiente para operar em cenГЎrios reais de produГ§ГЈo.\r\n\r\nA interface deve transmitir:\r\n\r\n* **ConfianГ§a**, por se tratar de uma loja funcional;\r\n* **Agilidade**, com foco em navegaГ§ГЈo rГЎpida e compra simples;\r\n* **Clareza**, por tambГ©m servir como vitrine tГ©cnica;\r\n* **Apelo comercial**, com ofertas, busca evidente e carrinho sempre acessГӯvel.\r\n\r\nA inspiraГ§ГЈo visual vem de lojas como **Mercado Livre**, **KaBuM** e **Magalu**, mas com identidade prГіpria, mais suave, limpa e moderna.\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\n## 2. Tema visual com Tailwind CSS 4\r\n\r\nA Shop API deve utilizar uma paleta suave, harmГҙnica e comercial, com tons claros para fundo, azul como cor principal de aГ§ГЈo e laranja para destaque de ofertas.\r\n\r\n### 2.1 Arquivo global de estilo\r\n\r\nExemplo sugerido para `app.css`, `globals.css` ou arquivo global equivalente:\r\n\r\n```css\r\n@import \"tailwindcss\";\r\n\r\n@theme {\r\n  /* Brand */\r\n  --color-shop-primary: #2563eb;\r\n  --color-shop-primary-hover: #1d4ed8;\r\n  --color-shop-primary-soft: #dbeafe;\r\n\r\n  --color-shop-secondary: #f97316;\r\n  --color-shop-secondary-hover: #ea580c;\r\n  --color-shop-secondary-soft: #ffedd5;\r\n\r\n  /* Base */\r\n  --color-shop-background: #f8fafc;\r\n  --color-shop-surface: #ffffff;\r\n  --color-shop-surface-muted: #f1f5f9;\r\n  --color-shop-border: #e2e8f0;\r\n\r\n  /* Text */\r\n  --color-shop-text: #0f172a;\r\n  --color-shop-text-muted: #64748b;\r\n  --color-shop-text-light: #94a3b8;\r\n  --color-shop-text-inverted: #ffffff;\r\n\r\n  /* Semantic */\r\n  --color-shop-success: #16a34a;\r\n  --color-shop-success-soft: #dcfce7;\r\n\r\n  --color-shop-warning: #f59e0b;\r\n  --color-shop-warning-soft: #fef3c7;\r\n\r\n  --color-shop-danger: #dc2626;\r\n  --color-shop-danger-soft: #fee2e2;\r\n\r\n  /* E-commerce */\r\n  --color-shop-price: #0f172a;\r\n  --color-shop-discount: #f97316;\r\n  --color-shop-free-shipping: #16a34a;\r\n  --color-shop-rating: #f59e0b;\r\n}\r\n```\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\n### 2.2 Uso das cores no Tailwind\r\n\r\n| Contexto                 | Classe Tailwind                              |\r\n| ------------------------ | -------------------------------------------- |\r\n| Fundo da aplicaГ§ГЈo       | `bg-shop-background`                         |\r\n| Cards e superfГӯcies      | `bg-shop-surface`                            |\r\n| SuperfГӯcie secundГЎria    | `bg-shop-surface-muted`                      |\r\n| Borda de cards e inputs  | `border-shop-border`                         |\r\n| Texto principal          | `text-shop-text`                             |\r\n| Texto secundГЎrio         | `text-shop-text-muted`                       |\r\n| Texto discreto           | `text-shop-text-light`                       |\r\n| BotГЈo principal          | `bg-shop-primary text-shop-text-inverted`    |\r\n| Hover do botГЈo principal | `hover:bg-shop-primary-hover`                |\r\n| BotГЈo de oferta          | `bg-shop-secondary text-shop-text-inverted`  |\r\n| Hover do botГЈo de oferta | `hover:bg-shop-secondary-hover`              |\r\n| Badge de oferta          | `bg-shop-secondary-soft text-shop-secondary` |\r\n| PreГ§o                    | `text-shop-price`                            |\r\n| Desconto                 | `text-shop-discount`                         |\r\n| Frete grГЎtis             | `text-shop-free-shipping`                    |\r\n| AvaliaГ§ГЈo                | `text-shop-rating`                           |\r\n| Mensagem de sucesso      | `bg-shop-success-soft text-shop-success`     |\r\n| Mensagem de alerta       | `bg-shop-warning-soft text-shop-warning`     |\r\n| Mensagem de erro         | `bg-shop-danger-soft text-shop-danger`       |\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\n## 3. Diretrizes de UI\r\n\r\n### Mobile First\r\n\r\nA interface deve ser pensada primeiro para telas pequenas. O mobile precisa ser direto, rГЎpido e com foco em compra.\r\n\r\nPrincГӯpios:\r\n\r\n* BotГөes grandes;\r\n* Busca sempre visГӯvel;\r\n* Carrinho sempre acessГӯvel;\r\n* Cards simples;\r\n* Menos texto por tela;\r\n* NavegaГ§ГЈo inferior opcional;\r\n* AГ§Гөes principais acima da dobra.\r\n\r\n### Desktop\r\n\r\nNo desktop, a interface pode usar melhor o espaГ§o horizontal.\r\n\r\nPrincГӯpios:\r\n\r\n* Header completo;\r\n* Busca centralizada;\r\n* Menu de categorias;\r\n* Grid com mais produtos;\r\n* Carrinho no canto superior direito;\r\n* ГҒrea do cliente com menu lateral;\r\n* PГЎgina de produto em duas colunas.\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\n## 4. Componentes globais\r\n\r\n### Header mobile\r\n\r\n```text\r\nв”Ңв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”җ\r\nв”Ӯ Shop API              рҹӣ’        в”Ӯ\r\nв”Ӯ в”Ңв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”җ в”Ӯ\r\nв”Ӯ в”Ӯ Buscar produto...        рҹ”Қ в”Ӯ в”Ӯ\r\nв”Ӯ в””в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”ҳ в”Ӯ\r\nв””в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”ҳ\r\n```\r\n\r\nClasses sugeridas:\r\n\r\n```html\r\n<header class=\"bg-shop-surface border-b border-shop-border\">\r\n  <div class=\"flex items-center justify-between px-4 py-3\">\r\n    <h1 class=\"text-xl font-bold text-shop-primary\">Shop API</h1>\r\n\r\n    <button class=\"relative text-shop-text\">\r\n      рҹӣ’\r\n    </button>\r\n  </div>\r\n\r\n  <div class=\"px-4 pb-4\">\r\n    <input\r\n      type=\"search\"\r\n      placeholder=\"Buscar produto...\"\r\n      class=\"w-full rounded-xl border border-shop-border bg-shop-background px-4 py-3 text-shop-text placeholder:text-shop-text-light\"\r\n    />\r\n  </div>\r\n</header>\r\n```\r\n\r\n### Header desktop\r\n\r\n```text\r\nв”Ңв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”җ\r\nв”Ӯ Shop API   [Buscar produtos...]   Ofertas  Categorias  рҹӣ’ рҹ‘Ө в”Ӯ\r\nв””в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”ҳ\r\n```\r\n\r\nClasses sugeridas:\r\n\r\n```html\r\n<header class=\"sticky top-0 z-50 border-b border-shop-border bg-shop-surface\">\r\n  <div class=\"mx-auto flex max-w-7xl items-center gap-6 px-6 py-4\">\r\n    <h1 class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-shop-primary\">Shop API</h1>\r\n\r\n    <input\r\n      type=\"search\"\r\n      placeholder=\"Buscar produtos...\"\r\n      class=\"flex-1 rounded-xl border border-shop-border bg-shop-background px-4 py-3 text-shop-text placeholder:text-shop-text-light\"\r\n    />\r\n\r\n    <nav class=\"flex items-center gap-4 text-sm font-medium text-shop-text-muted\">\r\n      <a class=\"hover:text-shop-primary\" href=\"/\">Ofertas</a>\r\n      <a class=\"hover:text-shop-primary\" href=\"/products\">Categorias</a>\r\n      <a class=\"hover:text-shop-primary\" href=\"/cart\">рҹӣ’</a>\r\n      <a class=\"hover:text-shop-primary\" href=\"/account\">рҹ‘Ө</a>\r\n    </nav>\r\n  </div>\r\n</header>\r\n```\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\n## 5. PГЎgina de Login\r\n\r\n### Objetivo\r\n\r\nPermitir que o cliente acesse sua conta com e-mail e senha, incluindo a opГ§ГЈo de manter-se conectado.\r\n\r\n### Mobile\r\n\r\n```text\r\nв”Ңв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”җ\r\nв”Ӯ Shop API                      в”Ӯ\r\nв”Ӯ Bem-vindo de volta            в”Ӯ\r\nв”Ӯ Acesse sua conta para comprar в”Ӯ\r\nв”Ӯ                               в”Ӯ\r\nв”Ӯ E-mail                        в”Ӯ\r\nв”Ӯ [_________________________]   в”Ӯ\r\nв”Ӯ                               в”Ӯ\r\nв”Ӯ Senha                         в”Ӯ\r\nв”Ӯ [_________________________]   в”Ӯ\r\nв”Ӯ                               в”Ӯ\r\nв”Ӯ [ ] Manter-me conectado       в”Ӯ\r\nв”Ӯ                               в”Ӯ\r\nв”Ӯ [Entrar]                      в”Ӯ\r\nв”Ӯ                               в”Ӯ\r\nв”Ӯ Esqueci minha senha           в”Ӯ\r\nв”Ӯ Criar nova conta              в”Ӯ\r\nв””в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”ҳ\r\n```\r\n\r\nClasses principais:\r\n\r\n```html\r\n<main class=\"min-h-screen bg-shop-background px-4 py-8\">\r\n  <section class=\"mx-auto max-w-sm rounded-2xl bg-shop-surface p-6 shadow-sm\">\r\n    <h1 class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-shop-primary\">Shop API</h1>\r\n    <h2 class=\"mt-6 text-xl font-semibold text-shop-text\">Bem-vindo de volta</h2>\r\n    <p class=\"mt-1 text-sm text-shop-text-muted\">Acesse sua conta para comprar.</p>\r\n\r\n    <form class=\"mt-6 space-y-4\">\r\n      <input class=\"w-full rounded-xl border border-shop-border px-4 py-3\" placeholder=\"E-mail\" />\r\n      <input class=\"w-full rounded-xl border border-shop-border px-4 py-3\" placeholder=\"Senha\" type=\"password\" />\r\n\r\n      <label class=\"flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-shop-text-muted\">\r\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" />\r\n        Manter-me conectado\r\n      </label>\r\n\r\n      <button class=\"w-full rounded-xl bg-shop-primary px-4 py-3 font-semibold text-shop-text-inverted hover:bg-shop-primary-hover\">\r\n        Entrar\r\n      </button>\r\n    </form>\r\n  </section>\r\n</main>\r\n```\r\n\r\n### Desktop\r\n\r\nLayout em duas colunas:\r\n\r\n* Coluna esquerda com mensagem institucional;\r\n* Coluna direita com card de login;\r\n* Fundo `bg-shop-background`;\r\n* Card `bg-shop-surface`;\r\n* BotГЈo principal `bg-shop-primary`.\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\n## 6. PГЎgina Home\r\n\r\n### Objetivo\r\n\r\nExibir ofertas, campo de busca, categorias e catГЎlogo de produtos.\r\n\r\n### Mobile\r\n\r\n```text\r\nв”Ңв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”җ\r\nв”Ӯ Shop API                  рҹӣ’  в”Ӯ\r\nв”Ӯ в”Ңв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”җ в”Ӯ\r\nв”Ӯ в”Ӯ Buscar produto...      рҹ”Қ в”Ӯ в”Ӯ\r\nв”Ӯ в””в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”ҳ в”Ӯ\r\nв”ңв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Ө\r\nв”Ӯ рҹ”Ҙ Ofertas da semana          в”Ӯ\r\nв”Ӯ в”Ңв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”җ в”Ӯ\r\nв”Ӯ в”Ӯ Banner promocional        в”Ӯ в”Ӯ\r\nв”Ӯ в”Ӯ AtГ© 40% OFF               в”Ӯ в”Ӯ\r\nв”Ӯ в””в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”ҳ в”Ӯ\r\nв”ңв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Ө\r\nв”Ӯ Categorias                    в”Ӯ\r\nв”Ӯ [Celulares] [Games] [Casa]    в”Ӯ\r\nв”ңв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Ө\r\nв”Ӯ Produtos em destaque          в”Ӯ\r\nв”Ӯ [Produto] [Produto]           в”Ӯ\r\nв”Ӯ [Produto] [Produto]           в”Ӯ\r\nв””в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”ҳ\r\n```\r\n\r\nClasses principais:\r\n\r\n```html\r\n<main class=\"bg-shop-background\">\r\n  <section class=\"px-4 py-4\">\r\n    <div class=\"rounded-2xl bg-shop-primary-soft p-5\">\r\n      <span class=\"rounded-full bg-shop-secondary-soft px-3 py-1 text-sm font-medium text-shop-secondary\">\r\n        Oferta da semana\r\n      </span>\r\n\r\n      <h2 class=\"mt-4 text-2xl font-bold text-shop-text\">\r\n        AtГ© 40% OFF em produtos selecionados\r\n      </h2>\r\n\r\n      <button class=\"mt-4 rounded-xl bg-shop-primary px-4 py-3 font-semibold text-shop-text-inverted hover:bg-shop-primary-hover\">\r\n        Ver ofertas\r\n      </button>\r\n    </div>\r\n  </section>\r\n</main>\r\n```\r\n\r\n### Desktop\r\n\r\n```text\r\nв”Ңв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”җ\r\nв”Ӯ Shop API   [Buscar produtos...]   Ofertas Categorias  рҹӣ’ рҹ‘Ө  в”Ӯ\r\nв”ңв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Ө\r\nв”Ӯ Menu categorias: Celulares | Games | InformГЎtica | Casa       в”Ӯ\r\nв”ңв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Ө\r\nв”Ӯ Banner principal                                              в”Ӯ\r\nв”ңв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Ө\r\nв”Ӯ Ofertas relГўmpago                                             в”Ӯ\r\nв”Ӯ [Produto] [Produto] [Produto] [Produto]                       в”Ӯ\r\nв”ңв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Ө\r\nв”Ӯ CatГЎlogo                                                      в”Ӯ\r\nв”Ӯ [Produto] [Produto] [Produto] [Produto]                       в”Ӯ\r\nв””в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв